snippet.title: Cat Leather Jackets | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
🎸 Cat Leather Jackets is a music game and visual novel about a teenage punk rock band. Follow Priya and her friends as they write, rehearse and perform songs, all the while dealing with the frustrations and drama of being young and trying to figure out what life is all about.

🚩 Get the game NOW on Steam:
https://bit.ly/catleatherjackets

🐱 Cat Leather Jackets is co-developed by diogoh3x, Garoa Studios and Kuating!

https://twitter.com/diogoh3x
https://twitter.com/kuating

Follow Garoa Studios on all platforms: https://linktr.ee/garoastudios
